infographic relation-dagre-flow-tb-badge-card
data
  title System overview
  desc Design-first control, native boundary, and backend split for one-DU MVP.
  nodes
    - id ops
      label Symphony / Codex / skills
      desc Decision support only
    - id ranctl
      label bin/ranctl
      desc Deterministic control entrypoint
    - id beam
      label BEAM control plane
      desc CU-CP, CU-UP, DU-high, actions
    - id observe
      label Observability / artifacts / config
      desc Evidence, telemetry, config views
    - id fapi
      label ran_fapi_core
      desc Canonical IR
    - id gateway
      label Native FAPI gateway
      desc Port sidecar
    - id local
      label local_du_low
      desc Local DU-low adapter path
    - id aerial
      label aerial_backend
      desc Future Aerial backend path
  relations
    ops -> ranctl
    ranctl -> beam
    ranctl -> observe
    beam -> fapi
    fapi -> gateway
    gateway -> local
    gateway -> aerial
theme
  palette #0f766e #1d4ed8 #0f172a #ea580c #475569 #7c3aed
  base
    text
      font-family Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif
